body_html:
Thank you lgeiger@ for filing the issue! This error was raised due to support not being added for multiple inputs and targets. I am working on a fix and will update this issue as soon as the fix is in.

You mentioned running into this issue when using dictionary as input. Currently DistributionStrategy requires a Dataset object as input to fit, evaluate and predict. Can you clarify how you were passing a dictionary? Thanks!
